Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.86,0:05:56.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先锋艇部队  全体出击
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.23,0:06:36.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾历奇  第二战队
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.91,0:06:38.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全舰炮侧瞄准
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.94,0:06:40.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白  开始炮侧瞄准
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.55,0:06:42.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炮侧瞄准完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.92,0:06:46.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.92,0:07:10.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,击毁
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.05,0:07:12.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功排除前方障碍物
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.31,0:07:13.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,航向无阻
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.42,0:07:16.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这样突破包围网
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.72,0:07:18.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战斗依然在持续
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.16,0:07:23.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一  第二战队似乎损失惨重
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.99,0:07:29.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两舷全速  航向10
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.62,0:07:31.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿越烟雾区域
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.12,0:07:40.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迅速调头上升
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.36,0:07:42.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全体乘员准备承受冲击！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.37,0:07:53.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.11,0:07:57.05,Gurakiesu,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发现敌方主力部队  在我舰正下方
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.17,0:08:08.54,Gurakiesu,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战场距离我方国境50
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.63,0:08:12.59,Gurakiesu,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,依然不断向我国境逼近
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.97,0:08:17.39,Gurakiesu,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未收到新的命令前维持现状  原地待命
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.47,0:08:18.60,Gurakiesu,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.34,0:08:24.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然…居然什么都做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.95,0:08:32.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法姆
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.56,0:08:36.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌舰转向10方向
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.91,0:08:39.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正往格拉吉艾斯国境线飞去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.62,0:08:41.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别让它跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.76,0:08:42.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.89,0:08:44.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让第四战队切断其后路
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.62,0:08:46.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对不要放跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.00,0:08:51.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第三及第四外层装甲区域中度损坏
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.05,0:08:53.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二号炮塔严重损毁
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.00,0:08:56.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前方国境附近出现大量敌军驱逐舰
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.87,0:09:00.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,航向不变  两舷全速
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.95,0:09:04.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不可以进来  法姆
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.16,0:09:06.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在还在战斗中
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.83,0:09:07.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回收先锋艇
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.51,0:09:10.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我也这样劝过她了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.75,0:09:12.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是捕鲸啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.84,0:09:14.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,捕鲸？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.50,0:09:16.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对  捕鲸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.80,0:09:20.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次我一定会履行契约的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.97,0:09:22.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是千载难逢的机会啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.96,0:09:24.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是么  舰长
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.87,0:09:28.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战斗中是无法回收先锋艇的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.39,0:09:30.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要靠自己回来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.86,0:09:50.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距格拉吉艾斯国境还有40
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.62,0:09:52.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前方敌舰队分散开了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.68,0:09:55.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌军发射了鱼雷
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.22,0:09:57.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立刻上升
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.55,0:09:58.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  要下降
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.93,0:10:00.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伸出头去会被当成靶子打的
