Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.82,0:10:03.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,潜入云中
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.26,0:10:10.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目标下降
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.71,0:10:11.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始潜行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.25,0:10:13.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌舰躲过了鱼雷攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.18,0:10:14.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要把它炸出来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.82,0:10:18.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全体舰队准备使用深水炸弹
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.53,0:10:20.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法姆  你不管吉赛尔了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.27,0:10:22.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没时间了  要出击了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.98,0:10:23.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.11,0:10:25.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米莉娅  戴好护目镜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.69,0:10:28.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么  究竟是怎么回…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.03,0:10:29.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米莉娅  要出击了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.18,0:10:32.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下  那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.86,0:10:33.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,起飞！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.05,0:10:38.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗…骗人的吧…
