Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.15,0:12:36.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完毕！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.64,0:12:40.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距离相撞还有3500
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.40,0:12:43.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赛西莉  寻找岩盘最薄的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.56,0:12:44.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
