Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.83,0:22:12.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我太感动了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.55,0:22:17.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜你  法姆
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.05,0:22:20.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米莉娅殿下也真厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.43,0:22:26.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于还是…成功使出了那招啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.33,0:22:39.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉泽  我做到了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.61,0:22:41.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这还是第一次成功办到哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.87,0:22:43.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泰蒂  吉赛尔
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.94,0:22:53.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜你  法姆
